---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Research"
  theme="research"
  description="Research areas and current projects."
>
  <section class="parallax-hero">
    <div class="hero-media" aria-hidden="true">
      <img
        class="hero-image"
        src="/images/research-divider.png"
        alt=""
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero-text glass">
          <p class="eyebrow">Research</p>
          <h1>Mechanistic insight into cytoskeletal machines.</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            I address long-standing questions about microtubule motors, dynamics,
            and other filaments using cryo-EM and single-molecule fluorescence
            microscopy, alongside computational analysis tools.
          </p>
          <div class="cta-row">
            <a class="btn primary" href="/cv/">View CV</a>
            <a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">Contact</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
          <h2>Active themes</h2>
          <div class="card-grid" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
            <div class="card">
              <h3>Motor mechanics</h3>
              <p class="meta">Mechanistic insight into dynein regulation on microtubules.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <h3>Microtubule dynamics</h3>
              <p class="meta">Polymerization, stability, and non-canonical structures.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <h3>Filament structure</h3>
              <p class="meta">Microtubule and ESCRT-III structures that drive remodeling.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <h3>Single-Molecule Biophysics</h3>
              <p class="meta">Fluorescence microscopy to probe motor behavior.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <h3>Cryo-EM analysis</h3>
              <p class="meta">CryoDRGN, Topaz, CrYOLO, Relion, and CryoSPARC for particle analysis.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <h3>Computational tool development</h3>
              <p class="meta">Custom pipelines for cryo-EM and single-molecule data analysis.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container publications-block">
      <div class="panel">
        <h2>Publications</h2>
        <div class="list">
        <div class="list-item">
          <strong>Asgard archaea reveal the conserved principles of ESCRT-III membrane remodeling</strong>
          <div class="meta">Souza DP*, Espadas J*, <span class="author-highlight">Chaaban S*</span>, Moody ERR, Hatano T, Balasubramanian M, Williams TA, Roux A, Baum B.</div>
          <div class="meta">Science Advances - 2025</div>
        </div>
        <div class="list-item">
          <strong>A force-sensitive mutation reveals a non-canonical role for dynein in anaphase progression</strong>
          <div class="meta">Salvador-Garcia D, Jin L, Hensley A, Golcuk M, Gallaud E, <span class="author-highlight">Chaaban S</span>, Port F, Vagnoni A, Planelles-Herrero VJ, McClintock MA, Derivery E, Carter AP, Giet R, Gur M, Yildiz A, Bullock SL.</div>
          <div class="meta">Journal of Cell Biology - 2024</div>
        </div>
        <div class="list-item">
          <strong>Navigating protein structure prediction in the era of machine learning</strong>
          <div class="meta"><span class="author-highlight">Chaaban S*</span>, Ratkeviciute G*, Lau C*.</div>
          <div class="meta">The Biochemist - 2024</div>
        </div>
        <div class="list-item">
          <strong>Structure of dynein-dynactin on microtubules shows tandem adaptor binding</strong>
          <div class="meta"><span class="author-highlight">Chaaban S</span>, Carter AP.</div>
          <div class="meta">Nature - 2022</div>
        </div>
        <div class="list-item">
          <strong>Crystal structure of human PACRG in complex with MEIG1 reveals roles in axoneme formation and tubulin binding</strong>
          <div class="meta">Khan N, Pelletier D, McAlear TS, Croteau N, Veyron S, Bayne A, Black C, Ichikawa I, Khalifa AAZ, <span class="author-highlight">Chaaban S</span>, Kurinov I, Brouhard GJ, Bechstedt S, Bui KH, Trempe J-F.</div>
          <div class="meta">Structure - 2021</div>
        </div>
        <div class="list-item">
          <strong>The structure and dynamics of C. elegans tubulin reveals the mechanistic basis of microtubule growth</strong>
          <div class="meta"><span class="author-highlight">Chaaban S</span>, Jariwala S, Hsu C-T, Redemann S, Kollman JM, Muller-Reichert T, Sept D, Bui KH, Brouhard GJ.</div>
          <div class="meta">Developmental Cell - 2018</div>
        </div>
        <div class="list-item">
          <strong>A microtubule bestiary: structural diversity in tubulin polymers</strong>
          <div class="meta"><span class="author-highlight">Chaaban S</span>, Brouhard GJ.</div>
          <div class="meta">Molecular Biology of the Cell - 2017</div>
        </div>
        <div class="list-item">
          <strong>The synthetic diazonamide DZ-2384 has distinct effects on microtubule curvature and dynamics without neurotoxicity</strong>
          <div class="meta">Wieczorek M, Tcherkezian J, Bernier C, Prota AE, <span class="author-highlight">Chaaban S</span>, Rolland Y, Godbout C, Hancock MA, Arezzo JC, Ocal O, Rocha C, Olieric N, Hall A, Ding H, Bramoulle A, Annis MG, Zogopoulos G, Harran PG, Wilkie TM, Brekken RA, Siegel PM, Steinmetz MO, Shore GC, Brouhard GJ, Roulston A.</div>
          <div class="meta">Science Translational Medicine - 2016</div>
        </div>
        <div class="list-item">
          <strong>Microtubule-associated proteins control the kinetics of microtubule nucleation</strong>
          <div class="meta">Wieczorek M, Bechstedt S, <span class="author-highlight">Chaaban S</span>, Brouhard GJ.</div>
          <div class="meta">Nature Cell Biology - 2015</div>
        </div>
        <div class="list-item">
          <strong>Macromolecular crowding pushes catalyzed microtubule growth to near the theoretical limit</strong>
          <div class="meta">Wieczorek M*, <span class="author-highlight">Chaaban S*</span>, Brouhard GJ.</div>
          <div class="meta">Cellular and Molecular Bioengineering - 2013</div>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .glass-panel {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--text) 6%, transparent);
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--text) 16%, transparent);
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
  }
  .parallax-hero {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: clamp(18rem, 8vh, 20rem) 0 4.5rem;
    width: 100vw;
    margin-left: calc(50% - 50vw);
  }

  .parallax-hero .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-media {
    position: fixed;
    top: var(--header-offset, 96px);
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    pointer-events: none;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .hero-image {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    object-position: center;
    transform: translateY(0);
    will-change: transform;
    filter: saturate(1.05);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: none;
  }

  .glass {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 65%, transparent);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .parallax-hero .hero {
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .parallax-hero .card {
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .parallax-hero .card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .publications-block {
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .parallax-hero {
      padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    }

    .glass {
      padding: 1.6rem;
    }

    .publications-block {
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .parallax-hero {
      padding: 6rem 0 3.5rem;
    }

    .hero-image {
      object-position: top center;
    }
  }

  .publications-block .list-item strong {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
  }

  .publications-block .list-item .meta {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .author-highlight {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
